\

### Equation {.unnumbered}

$$
θ(t)=θ_0​cos(ωt)
$$

$$
x(t)=L​sin(θ)
$$


$$
y(t)=−L​cos(θ)
$$

$$
ω=\sqrt{\frac{L}{g}}
$$


*Where:*,

- θ(t) = angular position;
- x(t) = *x* coordinate;
- y(t) = *y* coordinate;
- ω = angular frequency


